  <description>
    <p>
      Resonance is a clean and minimal API client application designed to provide an excellent
      user experience for testing and interacting with APIs. It offers a modern and intuitive
      interface for developers.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>OpenAPI/Swagger collection imports - Import OpenAPI 3.0 specifications in YAML or JSON format</li>
      <li>Variable templating system - Use template variables with {{ variableName }} syntax for API keys, base URLs, and more</li>
      <li>Multiple HTTP methods - Support for GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, and PATCH requests</li>
      <li>Request body schema generation - Automatically generate example request bodies from OpenAPI schemas</li>
      <li>Clean, organized interface - Split layout with collections sidebar and tabbed request/response sections</li>
      <li>Theme support - Light, dark, system, and blueprint themes with CSS custom properties</li>
      <li>Multi-language support - Available in English, German, Spanish, French, and Italian</li>
      <li>Secure architecture - Built with context isolation and secure IPC communication</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

